Match each class to its role (Product, Concrete Product, Creator, Concrete Creator):

```python
class Notification:
    def send(self): pass

class EmailNotification(Notification):
    def send(self): print("Email")

class Notifier:
    def create_notification(self): pass
    def notify(self):
        n = self.create_notification()
        n.send()

class EmailNotifier(Notifier):
    def create_notification(self): return EmailNotification()
```
